<p>This guideline updates a previous version: Halyard MY, Wasif N, Haffty BG, Harris EE, Arthur DW, Bailey L, Bellon JR, Carey L, Goyal S, Horst KC, MacDonald SM, Moran MS, Expert Panel on Radiation Oncology-Breast. ACR Appropriateness Criteria&reg; local-regional recurrence (LR) and salvage surgery -- breast cancer. [online publication]. Reston (VA): American College of Radiology (ACR); 2010. 8 p.</p></div></p>
