 (174.9), <a href="/web/20180712200603/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0337354&amp;fLockTerm=Resection+of+quadrant+of+breast">Resection of quadrant of breast</a>
 (85.22), <a href="/web/20180712200603/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0024885&amp;fLockTerm=Subtotal+mastectomy">Subtotal mastectomy</a>
