</table>
<p>Note: Abbreviations used in the tables are listed at the end of the "Major Recommendations" field.</p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Variant 2:</span> 42-year-old woman, 3.0-cm LRR in breast 6 years after BCT + chemotherapy for T1cN0 lesion. Biopsy showed invasive ductal carcinoma. ER/PR (&ndash;). HER-2 negative/nonamplified. EOD workup positive: liver and multiple bone metastases.</strong></p>
